name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Jane C. ORIE, Petitioner

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 27th day of September, 2011, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal and the Motion for Stay of Retrial Pending Disposition of Allocatur Petition, filed in the above matter, are each hereby DENIED.
Justice ORIE MELVIN did not participate in the consideration or decision of this matter.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
